Space Microwave LaboratoriesInc said it registered with the Securities and ExchangeCommission a secondary offering of 2,200 units of itssecurities at 1,000 dlrs per unit.    Each unit consists of shares of common stock, common stockpurchase warrants and 1,000-dlr principal amount of convertiblesubordinated debentures.    RLR Securities Group Inc will underwrite the offering. Reuter&#3;